{"id":"radicals","slug":"radicals-root-calculator","name":"Radicals & Roots Calculator","category":"algebra","icon":"√","description":"Calculate any nth root. Simplify radicals and compute radical expressions.","tags":["radical","root","nth root","algebra","simplify"],"fields":[{"id":"radicand","label":"Radicand (x)","type":"number","defaultValue":64,"constraint":{"step":0.01}},{"id":"index","label":"Root Index (n)","type":"number","defaultValue":3,"constraint":{"min":2,"max":20,"step":1}},{"id":"root","label":"ⁿ√x","type":"computed","precision":8,"helpText":"x^(1/n)"},{"id":"check","label":"(ⁿ√x)ⁿ ≈ x","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"sqrt","label":"√x (square root)","type":"computed","precision":6}],"groups":[{"id":"inputs","label":"Radical","fields":["radicand","index"]},{"id":"outputs","label":"Results","fields":["root","check","sqrt"]}],"formulas":{"root":"radicand >= 0 ? radicand^(1/index) : -(abs(radicand)^(1/index))","check":"(radicand >= 0 ? radicand^(1/index) : -(abs(radicand)^(1/index)))^index","sqrt":"sqrt(abs(radicand))"},"examples":[{"label":"∛64","inputs":{"radicand":64,"index":3}},{"label":"⁴√256","inputs":{"radicand":256,"index":4}},{"label":"⁵√-32","inputs":{"radicand":-32,"index":5}}]}
